snippet.title: Spellrazor Game Trailer
snippet.description:
http://dene.itch.io/spellrazor
http://gamejolt.com/games/spellrazor/123648

Trailer for 'Spellrazor', a haunted arcade game from 1981, now available for PC and Mac. 
Spellrazor is a roguelike-lite shooter with 27 fire buttons, bullet-time, secret adventure game and super creepy back-story.
